HOW TO USE:
-----------

New Setup:
  1. cp .env.example .env (and edit with your API keys)
  2. make install
  3. make setup
  4. make start (chat server)
  5. make web-ui (admin portal)

Daily Use:
  - make start      # Start the chat server
  - make web-ui     # Start the admin web UI
  - make kill-server # Stop all servers
  - make inspect-db # View database stats
  - make help       # See all commands

